# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Third-party COPYRIGHTED study content — MUST NOT be committed.
# Cambridge IELTS tests/audio/figures, Oxford 5000, PHaVE (see NOTICE / README).
# Local builds still work: MSBuild reads these from disk; they just never enter
# Git. AWL/AVL seeds (CC0) are intentionally NOT ignored. Before making the repo
# public, externalise content so a fresh clone builds without these files.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Listening — Cambridge audio, maps, transcripts, test JSON
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Ielts.Listening/Seed/Audio/
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Ielts.Listening/Seed/Images/
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Ielts.Listening/Seed/Transcripts/
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Ielts.Listening/Seed/ielts_listening_tests.json

# Reading — Cambridge passages/questions + figures
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Ielts.Reading/Seed/Images/
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Ielts.Reading/Seed/ielts_reading_tests.json

# Writing — Cambridge prompts + Task 1 figures
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Ielts.Writing/Seed/Images/
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Ielts.Writing/Seed/writing_tests.json

# Dictionary — Oxford 5000 (OUP) and PHaVE
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Dictionary/Seed/oxford_5000.json
src/EnglishStudio.Modules.Dictionary/Seed/phave.json

# AI rubrics — derived from official IELTS public band descriptors (copyright). Shipped via the
